    "Participants answer the question: \"Given the quality of the information available, how confident am I in my own judgments?\"",
    "The response options were a three-point scale from high to medium to low.",
    "This probability and confidence measure and its scales follow the guidelines of the NATO Allied Joint Doctrine for Intelligence Procedures (NATO, 2016).",
    "They are summarized in Table 1.",
    "Figure 5 shows examples of items from both parts of the analysis task."
